source: hh/tests/cli_conformance.rs
expression: "String::from_utf8_lossy(&out.stdout)"
---
Print non-interactive detail about a session (SRS FR-4)

Usage: hh inspect [OPTIONS] [SESSION]

Arguments:
  [SESSION]  Session short id, full id, or `last`

Options:
      --step <STEP>  Print the full detail of step N
      --json         Emit stable, documented JSON (single object with --step, NDJSON stream otherwise)
      --diff         Print the concatenated unified diff of file changes
      --failed       Jump to the first error/failed step
  -h, --help         Print help

Example:
  hh inspect last
  hh inspect a1b2c3 --step 7
  hh inspect last --json | jq
  hh inspect last --diff
